{"tid":575210,"cid":35,"subCid":0,"title":"點用最抵嘅價錢喺外地聽香港嘅來電","createTime":"2018-02-28T05:12:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-28T07:04:05.000Z","uid":12697,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"07a311827202e13a5254841148d5ed1554c689ed","tid":575210,"uid":12697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T05:12:49.000Z","msg":"嚟緊會去外地2個禮拜，唔算miss咗啲重要電話（搵工中），有無巴打知道點樣可以抵嘅價錢聽香港電話？<br />\n<br />\nGoogle 過知SMT有個app (一櫞兩號）可以飛線去一個電話再用data嚟接聽，但我唔係SMT 用戶，一俾要成年咁俾（$35X)<br />\n<br />\n另一個方法係用Skype，但如果我飛線去Skype 嗰no. 飛線嗰下會唔會已經當咗我係打緊IDD??<br />\n<br />\n我用緊Sun mobile, 如果用佢個漫遊，一分鐘就已經$1X<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔該巴打們幫吓我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果Trivago 可以話我知點用最抵嘅價錢搵到最好嘅IDD方法就好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"383f35336afe7cf0d214107680e58ec5dac2d576","tid":575210,"uid":169765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T07:04:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}